<a href="/questions/608194-because-this-book-doesn-t-include-book-of">Because this book doesn&#39;t include &#39;Book of Imaginary Beings,&#39; it&#39;s obviously not a COMPLETE collection of his fictions. What other stories or collections are excluded from this collection?</a>
</div>
