        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer214472178" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2265394414610331889">Do yourself a massive favor and read Borges. He can deliver more plot and twists in 2-5 pages than many authors do in 300. Every page will blow your mind as you loose yourself in the brilliant labyrinth of his words. Read it. Now.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


