        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer425481507" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3888210304912855735">I was hesitant to post anything about this book. Given the stature of Borges it would have been easier just to pretend that I&apos;d never read it. Well, the truth is I hardly did read it. I found his style impenetrable. For me there was no way into these stories, I was just stuck on the outside, with a book full of words on my lap.</span>
  <span id="freeText3888210304912855735" style="display:none">I was hesitant to post anything about this book. Given the stature of Borges it would have been easier just to pretend that I'd never read it. Well, the truth is I hardly did read it. I found his style impenetrable. For me there was no way into these stories, I was just stuck on the outside, with a book full of words on my lap.</span>
